videos.description: Cardinals' Lamar Jackson runs the ball 22 yards for the early touchdown.
videos.headline: Louisville's Jackson sprints for first TD of game

videos.description: Florida State's James Blackman makes a great throw to Nyqwan Murray for 37 yards.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Blackman shows off the touch with 37-yard throw

videos.description: James Blackman finds Ryan Izzo wide open in the end zone to tie the game in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Blackman finds Izzo for TD

videos.description: James Blackman finds Ryan Izzo wide open again for a 30-yard completion.
videos.headline: Florida State's Blackman completes 30-yard pass

videos.description: James Blackman finds Auden Tate on the sideline who makes a nice catch.
videos.headline: Blackman throws a dime under pressure

videos.description: Seminoles' James Blackman is sacked by Henry Famurewa for a loss of 5 yards.
videos.headline: Florida State's Blackman is sacked

videos.description: Louisville Lamar Jackson fumbles the ball, and its recovered by Seminoles' Matthew Thomas who returns it for a 34-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jackson's fumble leads to Seminoles TD

videos.description: Cardinals' Lamar Jackson quickly bounces back and finds Seth Dawkins for a 26-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Louisville's Jackson finds Dawkins in end zone for TD

videos.description: Seminoles' James Blackman pass is intercepted by Trumaine Washington who returns it for 22 yards.
videos.headline: Louisville picks off  Blackman

videos.description: Seminoles' head coach Jimbo Fisher praises Lamar Jackson and says they now need to get points on offense.
videos.headline: FSU head coach discusses Jackson's performance

videos.description: James Blackman finds Auden Tate who then drags the defender for the  first down.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Tate carries defender

videos.description: Cardinals' Lamar Jackson avoids multiple defenders with a nice spin move for the 51-yard gain.
videos.headline: Jackson with a great 51-yard run

videos.description: Cardinals' Reggie Bonnafon runs straight up the middle to take the lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Bonnafon's TD gives Louisville the lead

videos.description: Louisville's Trumaine Washington picks off James Blackman's pass and returns the ball for 22 yards.
videos.headline: Cardinals' Washington picks off Blackman

videos.description: Lamar Jackson hands the ball off to Dae Williams who runs 25 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Williams TD extends Louisville's lead

videos.description: Seminoles' Jacques Patrick runs for 6 yards and fumbles the ball on the 1-yard line, and its recovered by Nyqwan Murray for a touchdown.
videos.headline: FSU fumbles the ball and recovers it for TD

videos.description: FSU James Blackman finds Nyqwan Murray for a 20-yard touchdown to tie the game in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Seminoles' tie game with Murray TD

videos.description: On 4th down, Lamar Jackson pass is incomplete to Dez Fitzpatrick in the end zone.
videos.headline: Ball slips through Fitzpatrick's hands in the end zone

videos.description: James Blackman fumbles the ball and it is recovered by Louisville's Henry Famurewa.
videos.headline: Blackman turns the ball over late in the 4th

videos.description: Cardinals K Blanton Creque hits the 34-yard field goal to give Louisville a win over Florida State.
videos.headline: Louisville wins game with field goal

videos.description: Lamar Jackson discusses how the team stayed together and  kept fighting in Louisville's 31-28 win over Florida State.
videos.headline: Lamar Jackson discusses win in Tallahassee

videos.description: Cardinals' Lamar Jackson fakes a hand off and runs the ball 15 yards for a first down.
videos.headline: Jackson leads Louisville down field with run

videos.description: Lamar Jackson accounts for two touchdowns and a late field goal lifts Louisville past Florida State 31-28.
videos.headline: Louisville squeaks by Florida State
